<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>About <%= shopData.shopName %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/main.css" />
  </head>

  <body class="about-body">

    <div class="about-container">
      <h1>About <%= shopData.shopName %></h1>

      <p class="about-tagline">
        Your personalised vitamin store — helping you understand what your body really needs.
      </p>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          At <strong><%= shopData.shopName %></strong>, our mission is to make health simple.  
          Instead of guessing which vitamins might help you, we provide a personalised experience  
          that identifies your nutritional needs and recommends the supplements that suit you best.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>
          We combine convenience with smart technology:
        </p>
        <ul class="about-list">
          <li>✔ Create a free account to get started</li>
          <li>✔ Take our personalised vitamin quiz</li>
          <li>✔ Instantly receive a recommendation based on your answers</li>
          <li>✔ Add your recommended vitamins to your cart and save them for later</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <p>
          Our shop provides a curated selection of high-quality vitamins and minerals designed to support:
        </p>
        <ul class="about-list">
          <li>✔ Energy and metabolism</li>
          <li>✔ Immunity and overall wellness</li>
          <li>✔ Mood, focus, and stress support</li>
          <li>✔ Women’s and men’s general health</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>
          Choosing supplements can feel overwhelming — that’s why we focus on clarity,  
          simplicity, and personalisation. Our quiz-based recommendations remove the guesswork  
          so you only purchase vitamins that match your unique needs. Your health journey  
          should be tailored to you, and we’re here to support every step.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
